<!-- @format -->

Step 1: Create public repo
Step 2: Add the base(repo name to vite.config.js) e.g: base: '/your-repo-name/', above plugins.
Step 3: vite build
Step 4: Push the dist to gh-pages branch: npm install gh-pages --save-dev
Step 5: Add a script to package.json: "scripts": {
"build": "vite build",
"deploy": "gh-pages -d dist"
}
Step 6: npm run build
npm run deploy
